Our guest toiletries collection at The Raviz Ashtamudi uses olive-based surfactants, pure essential oils & authentic shea butter. The luxury line with White Tea & Tangerine is the perfect combination of sustainability and sophistication by being Paraben-free, dermatologically safe & most importantly 100% cruelty-free and vegan.
